Text: Finally, Northern Trust Corp grew its stake in shares of Travelers Companies by 1.4% in the second quarter. Northern Trust Corp now owns 3,618,718 shares of the insurance provider's stock worth $541,070,000 after acquiring an additional 51,281 shares during the last quarter.
